{"tid":1313282,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"37個月以來 我們都走得好苦","createTime":"2019-07-13T17:20:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T21:07:36.000Z","uid":223545,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4d53321606117a492da3c811fc3c575988bed13b","tid":1313282,"uid":223545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T17:20:37.000Z","msg":"13/7/2019，係我地兩個拍拖嘅第37個月<br />\n<br />\n我地由中學拍拖拍到依家<br />\n少不免有「拍拖拍到好攰」嘅諗法<br />\n但為左段感情可以升温<br />\n我就諗住係第37個月比啲小surprise佢<br />\n諗住多返些少儀式感<br />\n<br />\n拍拖第37個月 <br />\n我送左對鞋比佢<br />\n琴日我由7點等到佢11點放工<br />\n<br />\n終於等到佢放工<br />\n我送對鞋比佢<br />\n佢一句多謝 一個擁抱 都無<br />\n佢仲諗住我送完比佢 我就自己搭返車走<br />\n一句關心我嘅說話都無<br />\n<br />\n其實早幾個月佢已經冷暴力我<br />\n明明佢追我先<br />\n但追到手又咁冷漠<br />\n係想點...<br />\n我都會唔開心架<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n/若不是你突然闖進我生活<br />\n我怎會把死守的寂寞放任了/"},{"pid":"4942274c9890dcf44bc4e87b5490c7de364c9e78","tid":1313282,"uid":112702,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T21:55:52.000Z","msg":"其實一冷暴力 已經可以講玩完"},{"pid":"4dc98e498fd65159fc4119108a8a87f7797b2fe6","tid":1313282,"uid":22558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T02:47:33.000Z","msg":"算把啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a26d7b9fe0e0886843b5a6143b475c552dec7d6a","tid":1313282,"uid":223545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4942274c9890dcf44bc4e87b5490c7de364c9e78","tid":1313282,"uid":112702,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T21:55:52.000Z","msg":"其實一冷暴力 已經可以講玩完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T05:34:33.000Z","msg":"佢係咪淡左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"899315726b66b0612dc6615823885a16ccb778c1","tid":1313282,"uid":223545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4dc98e498fd65159fc4119108a8a87f7797b2fe6","tid":1313282,"uid":22558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T02:47:33.000Z","msg":"算把啦<i